Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.44,0:00:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于能遇见了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不幸丢失的部份
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于能遇见了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直缺失的部份
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.60,0:00:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而将其毁掉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.13,0:01:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.66,0:01:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.55,0:01:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你是不可饶恕的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.05,0:01:37.61,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,絶望的に君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.76,0:01:44.81,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,反転する世界のプラトニック 愛し合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:02:00.46,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,僕らが見てる世界は いつでも逆さまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.28,0:02:10.93,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,どうしようもないことで たいがい決まってく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:23.01,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,涙するほど傷つく瞳 心で叫びながら黙っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:33.60,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,最後のふたり 混ざれないまま 秒読みが聞こえてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:39.76,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,絶望的に君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:45.61,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,すたれゆく動物みたいに愛し合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:49.98,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,泣きたいくらい君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:53.32,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,反転する世界のプラトニック
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:56.33,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,感じたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.05,0:01:37.61,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,你美得令人绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.76,0:01:44.81,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们在倒错的精神世界中相爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:02:00.46,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我们眼里的世界总是相互颠倒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.28,0:02:10.93,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,这几乎要被认定为是无可奈何的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:23.01,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,伤口淌泪的眼眸 在内心沉默地叫喊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:33.60,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的两人来不及结合便听到离别的倒数
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:39.76,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,你美得令人绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:45.61,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们像渐趋衰老的动物一样相爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:49.98,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,你美得令人落泪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:53.32,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,在倒错的精神世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:56.33,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我想细细体会…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}亚当的断片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出云那家伙 竟敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希尔菲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希尔菲 我最可恶的臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我唯独不能失去你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕这个世界变成什么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死神?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.37,0:03:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把我叫做死神?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.61,0:03:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死神…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你才对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不完整的机械天使
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么能听到他的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.05,0:04:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为原本我就是你 你就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此我无法原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其无法原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.23,0:04:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你杀害了我们的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲? 你说的是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是Altair的最高领导者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出云
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.11,0:04:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你 一切都…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胆小鬼阿马塔给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然一个人就能合体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:05:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能办到 我没理由办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 我办到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.46,0:05:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被一分为二的灵魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邂逅了机械天使的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:06:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻正是红色的梦境与蓝色的现实相会之际
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.70,0:06:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克雷雅理事长 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红色的行星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.15,0:06:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Altair
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:55.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捕捉到GEPART的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎正在与Abductor战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:06:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.62,0:07:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受我吧 Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空间填补
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安迪 再说服下去也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续使用能力的话 你的身体会…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么放弃的话 那Mix怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会放弃的 Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到用这双手紧抱你为止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙 为什么要为了我做到这种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.93,0:07:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想填满你的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌洞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最讨厌你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.02,0:08:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了 安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.48,0:08:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去你会被Mix捏碎的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.98,0:08:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在以我填满你心中裂开的大洞之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我心中的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.25,0:08:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.15,0:09:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于能抱到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记忆的缺失部分正逐渐被填补
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所失去的…身为女人的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 一直出现在我记忆里的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.57,0:09:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.71,0:09:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你恢复记忆了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安迪 我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.23,0:09:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:09:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:09:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.39,0:10:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身体变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经…不是女孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使这样也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是男是女这无关紧要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢的就是Mix这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以跟你合体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.31,0:10:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 合体是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们明白现在是什么状况吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.72,0:10:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我坚守至今的纯洁灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经我千锤百炼的节操
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今正是让其爆发之时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:10:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夙愿合体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:10:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Go
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.98,0:11:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐 无论是爸爸还是妈妈都伴随在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在Altair这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我不同 你身处在拥有一切的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可你却…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不记得有被父母养育过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.31,0:11:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我养大的是未影 那个恶魔般的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和他一起的生活是异常的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:12:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在未影身边 我感到比独处时更加孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.59,0:12:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁也无法信任
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.15,0:12:15.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但第一次闻到臭女人…希尔菲的味道时我感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,0:12:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世上只有这个女人能够接受我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.85,0:12:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是我命中注定的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀了希尔菲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秉承爱的名义 跟她互相残杀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕要为此牺牲那对我只生不养的所谓亲生父母
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:33.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我软弱的心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是软弱的 你的爱也是软弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以一万两千年前我们才会和希尔菲天涯相隔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.53,0:12:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后在一万两千年前后的现世
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:12:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就眼看着母亲离去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次又要把希尔菲给…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 不是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.49,0:13:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Altair进一步接近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且在不断加速
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.75,0:13:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像和互相碰撞的阿马塔他们取得共鸣一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理事长?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.92,0:13:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是撰写在创圣之书里的新篇章
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.19,0:13:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一分为二的灵魂在彼此呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两颗星球亦随之相互牵引
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终交相碰撞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陈旧的事物将会消失殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,崭新的世界将会应运而生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个未影将成为神的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所期待的未来也是那样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像你一直在守望着这颗星球一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一直在注视着你所选择的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:15.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我一直注视着于任何时候都岿然不动的你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这样真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了崭新的世界 当今的生命将全部成为牺牲品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.25,0:14:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个学园的一众学生也不会例外
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为那是创圣之书所追求的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就一动不动地迎接大家的死亡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.72,0:14:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的觉得这样就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不动·ZEN
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.57,0:14:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我初次邂逅御子乃的时候也觉得那是命运使然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.11,0:15:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是能接受我、和我感受到同样痛苦的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我对她的印象并不止这些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃她很怯弱 容易生气 又爱莫名其妙地吃醋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.68,0:15:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许你夸奖臭女人!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.97,0:15:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但御子乃她又总是努力不懈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够体谅别人的痛苦 能够让大家团结一心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是希尔菲 而是现在的御子乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一派胡言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.72,0:15:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我最喜欢的!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:52.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要一手掌握命运
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.66,0:15:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要连命运也一并超越 拥抱现在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.63,0:16:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃（希尔菲）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.36,0:16:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔和那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不能够战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔 神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能战斗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否定战斗就相当于否定这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是和他们而是要和我合体哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.19,0:16:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃·铃白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.05,0:16:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.41,0:16:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是 爱的失败者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.15,0:17:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两万四千年前 跟我缔有婚约的男人背叛了我的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.53,0:17:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怀揣着这份仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.45,0:17:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和阿波罗尼亚斯的转世阿波罗战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那时我还未能完全割舍那挥之不去的爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿波罗为了拯救世界而希望与我合为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我对此予以了接受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想到要和深爱的人合为一体 我就感到欣喜若狂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我在灵魂相融的那一瞬间察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿波罗并不是阿波罗尼亚斯的转世
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的阿波罗尼亚斯是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿波罗尼亚斯一而再地践踏了我的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要将两颗星球合而为一 并成为新世界的神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.74,0:18:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱的失败者将毁灭所有的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我所追求的新神话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 我们合为一体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀死多少次也不足以解恨的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从我身边夺走阿波罗尼亚斯的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恨的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.78,0:18:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是复仇的婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是希尔菲的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:23.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那机体是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.95,0:19:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃…御子乃在那机体里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.51,0:19:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要更多的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Iron C 将母星的力量赐予我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.77,0:20:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未影 是打算吸光星球的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔 你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪炎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚叶 还有诸井
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.41,0:20:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你代替我合体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有你的Element能力 就无法和那些家伙对抗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔同学 我们合体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决战合体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.22,0:20:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,GO Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.99,0:20:45.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion EVOL
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.79,0:20:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把御子乃还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.41,0:20:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:21:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Iron C 制裁他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.80,0:21:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区翼犬休想能反抗神的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:13.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后神乐…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.29,0:21:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.16,0:21:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐 你是不能反抗我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:21:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蹂躏合体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.05,0:21:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,GO Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.63,0:22:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 多么美丽 又多么空虚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.75,0:22:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.81,0:22:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色的…Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-------------------ED-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:57.93,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}君へ続く坂道に 白い花が咲いてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.07,0:23:05.74,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}夢から覚めたあとも 悲しい空見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.23,0:23:15.72,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}この気持ち葉っぱの裏に住んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.58,0:23:25.22,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}朝露が落ちる音に 耳をすませてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.41,0:23:33.08,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}神様 あなたが造った世界は 完璧じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.29,0:23:40.67,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}ここでは毎日恋がポロポロ 死んでゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.87,0:23:44.86,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}はじめて好きになったの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.01,0:23:48.02,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}あなたは知らないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.15,0:23:52.55,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}地球の裏側でいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.73,0:23:55.76,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}そばにいてほしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.95,0:24:00.09,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}私を忘れてもいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.31,0:24:06.60,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}そばにいてほしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:57.93,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}延伸到你身旁的坡道 点缀着雪白的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.07,0:23:05.74,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}从睡梦中惊醒之后 远望着忧伤的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.23,0:23:15.72,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}这份青涩的感觉 依存在绿叶错综的纹路之间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.58,0:23:25.22,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}侧耳聆听 晨露缓缓落下的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.41,0:23:33.08,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}神明您所创造的这个世界并不完美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.29,0:23:40.67,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}因为这里每天都有恋情一段接一段地告终
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.87,0:23:44.86,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我是初尝恋爱的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.01,0:23:48.02,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}这个你应该不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.15,0:23:52.55,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}即便永不见天日也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.73,0:23:55.76,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我只希望你留在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.95,0:24:00.09,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}就算你把我忘却也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.31,0:24:06.60,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我只希望你留在我身边
