Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.32,0:24:14.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得以相遇的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.18,0:24:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不停走过的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.59,0:24:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 篆刻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.78,0:24:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 祈祷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.48,0:24:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 合为一体吧
